Vice President Joe Biden released a statement expressing his condolences to the family of former Senator Ted Stevens, who had recently passed away. Biden mentioned that he and Stevens had a close bond and had shared similar family tragedies. He also mentioned that they had celebrated joyous moments together, such as the births of their daughters, which occurred just a few days apart. Biden acknowledged that they had served together for over 30 years but emphasized that Stevens was also his friend, and he will be missed.